{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-press-release-tsx","path":"/ar/media-center/qcdc-wraps-up-successful-first-edition-of-career-academy","result":{"data":{"contentfulPagePressRelease":{"id":"a4160a10-bd78-506f-8928-b5cdf148a175","slug":"qcdc-wraps-up-successful-first-edition-of-career-academy","title":"مركز قطر للتطوير المهني يختتم الدورة الافتتاحية من \"أكاديمية المهن\"","date":"2019-07-11","filterTags":null,"filterEntity":[{"contentful_id":"2LTdoMooBa6w04sioQY2ue"}],"heroImage":null,"modulesWrapper":[{"modules":[{"__typename":"ContentfulModuleBodyText","id":"8e7e7c56-4cc1-5b5d-be7c-75f0a014c9fe","text":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>اختتم مركز قطر للتطوير المهني، عضو مؤسسة قطر للتربية والعلوم وتنمية المجتمع، أنشطة الدورة الافتتاحية من برنامجه المطور \"أكاديمية المهن\"، الذي استقطب ما يقرب من 60 طالبًا وطالبة من المرحلة الثانوية، شاركوا في برامج متنوعة، تعرفوا خلالها على المسارات المهنية المتاحة أمامهم.</p>"}}},{"__typename":"ContentfulModuleImageGallery","id":"3bebc491-5103-500b-85fc-925224233d8d","images":[{"caption":null,"image":{"id":"e7094dfc-1968-509e-b1c5-6f93e9bc6eb3","title":"Career Academy Image 3","file":{"details":{"image":{"width":1639,"height":1092}}},"sizes":{"aspectRatio":1.8666666666666667,"src":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/7JkjAgikrJP69nzT96p9ku/d075cdab28549734fbf6b540fe21e240/Career_Academy_Image_3.jpg?w=1120&h=600&q=85","srcSet":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/7JkjAgikrJP69nzT96p9ku/d075cdab28549734fbf6b540fe21e240/Career_Academy_Image_3.jpg?w=280&h=150&q=85 280w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/7JkjAgikrJP69nzT96p9ku/d075cdab28549734fbf6b540fe21e240/Career_Academy_Image_3.jpg?w=560&h=300&q=85 560w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/7JkjAgikrJP69nzT96p9ku/d075cdab28549734fbf6b540fe21e240/Career_Academy_Image_3.jpg?w=1120&h=600&q=85 1120w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/7JkjAgikrJP69nzT96p9ku/d075cdab28549734fbf6b540fe21e240/Career_Academy_Image_3.jpg?w=1639&h=878&q=85 1639w","srcWebp":"//images.